hopobject.body: Your cash is being counted buy celexa online "This study provides an important initial observation of discrimination based on sexual orientation at the threshold stage of the rental transaction and is a point of departure for future research on housing discrimination against same-sex couples," the report says. HUD conducted 6,833 email correspondence tests in 50 metropolitan markets throughout the country. For each test, researchers sent two emails to the housing provider, but the only difference was the sexual orientation of the couple making the inquiry.
